{"tid":1619571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［致所有和理非］如果想保護勇武，請每日出街戴口罩","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:25:02.000Z","uid":119729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"692c755e332e95fb67b5dbea6bd433fa8fc560e8","tid":1619571,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"李家超：以下三種情況都不准蒙面<br />\n<br />\n1. 經警方批准的集會與遊行<br />\n2. 未經批准的集結<br />\n3. 非法集結與暴動<br />\n<br />\n違例者最高監禁 1 年、罰款 $25,000。蒙面包括遮蓋面部的任何物料，包括顏料。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n如在公眾地方蒙面，被警方截查而拒絕除下面罩，違例者最高監禁 6 個月、罰款 $10,000。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足唔會怕緊急法，<br />\n今次立法主要係針對和理非。<br />\n<br />\n你可以唔犯法，可以唔上前線，<br />\n但係唔好因爲咁怕左呢個極權。<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油</span>"},{"pid":"f19fd656f203c1786faba31938a8f5581da21042","tid":1619571,"uid":1411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"港共最大核彈已上水 求文宣&amp;外國手足火力全開!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616143</a>"},{"pid":"ee90c1698f7e3a4fff402189bef66950d36acc89","tid":1619571,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"全民戴口罩"},{"pid":"d184dc47cf84c3567547124744509638b8a22239","tid":1619571,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"面對極權<br />\n唔可以有半分軟弱"},{"pid":"ea782e71c98a7f9beaae13dc2443a1945548e058","tid":1619571,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">驅逐共匪 香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"3666eff12da3a2d2ec9365acc4f91a913a68933b","tid":1619571,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk